        .main__information__details__set__reason
          スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
      .main__information__details__set
        .main__information__details__set__picture
          = image_tag '/pict-reason-02.jpg', class: 'main__information__details__set__picture__img'
          .main__information__details__set__picture__number
            2
        .main__information__details__set__title
          %span.main__information__details__set__title--span
            シンプル
          で使いやすい
        .main__information__details__set__reason
          めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
      .main__information__details__set--last
        .main__information__details__set__picture
          = image_tag '/pict-reason-03.jpg', class: 'main__information__details__set__picture__img'
          .main__information__details__set__picture__number
            3
        .main__information__details__set__title
          手数料
          %span.main__information__details__set__title--span
            業界最安
