  .main__appeal
    .main__appeal__inner
      .main__appeal__inner__title
        会員数日本一位
      .main__appeal__inner__text
        FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。<br>出品・購入回数も業界最多です！<br>ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
      .main__appeal__inner__icons
        .main__appeal__inner__icons__appstore
          = image_tag '/appstore.svg', class: "main__appeal__inner__icons__appstore__logo"
        .main__appeal__inner__icons__googleplay
          = image_tag '/googleplay.svg', class: "main__appeal__inner__icons__googleplay__logo"
  .main__feature
    .main__feature__title
      FURIMAの特徴
    .main__feature__bar
    .main__feature__details
      .main__feature__details__set
        .main__feature__details__set__picture
          = image_tag '/icon-01.png', class: 'main__feature__details__set__picture__img'
        .main__feature__details__set__title
          簡単に売り買いできる
        .main__feature__details__set__text
          スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
      .main__feature__details__set
        .main__feature__details__set__picture
          = image_tag '/icon-03.png', class: 'main__feature__details__set__picture__img'
        .main__feature__details__set__title
          売上金は即日振込みに対応
        .main__feature__details__set__text
          午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
      .main__feature__details__set
        .main__feature__details__set__picture
          = image_tag '/icon-04.png', class: 'main__feature__details__set__picture__img'
        .main__feature__details__set__title
          様々な支払いに対応
        .main__feature__details__set__text
          お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
  - if @items.present?
    .main__pickup
      .main__pickup__title
        新規投稿商品
      .main__pickup__bar
      .main__pickup__box
        .main__pickup__box__items
          - @items.each do |item|
            .main__pickup__box__items__item
              .main__pickup__box__items__item__picture
                = link_to item_path(item) do
                  = image_tag item.photos[0].variant(auto_orient: true), class: 'main__pickup__box__items__item__picture__img'
              .main__pickup__box__items__item__list
                .main__pickup__box__items__item__list__name
                  = item.name
                .main__pickup__box__items__item__list__price
                  = "#{item.price}円"
